values:
here's where it's at now bitches

http://snideself.blogdrive.com/ 

hit it and quit it

I considered coming here and ranting a raving about how shitty everyone is, but that's extremely petty, so I'll keep it short. All I'm going to say is that I'm over it. I'm over this house, I'm over the people in it, I'm over Pgh, I'm over college, I'm over this life and all that is existence. Never in my life have I been so unhappy for such a long period of time.  I'm constantly trapped in absolutely ridiculous situations with equally nonsensical people. Fucking hell.  It's really wearing...
Man o man did I just have the sleep to end all sleeps.  I slept so hard my like body feels strange.  It was pretty awesome.  I'm still tired as nuts. Damn.

Well, it looks like America's favorite holiday is over in about 5.  I can say I had a really excellent day.  I got some bad ass cards from some hella awesome people (Thanks by the way), a flower that's now sitting in a sugar dispenser, a box of love from home, the cutest email ever, 8 hrs of decent sleep, and an iMix that covers all areas of Valentine's Day.  This Valentine's Day is pretty high up there. Alas, it has come to an end, but it was rad to the max!

"I had the deepest sleep ever last night. Infact I am still in bed as I write this. Almost like dying and being ressurected.

I dont drink alcohol, but sometimes I wonder when I have these really deep sleeps, if it like when someone gets drunk and passes out? The way TV and the movies make it seem is that when you are drunk, you have the most undisturbed sleep.

Why do I sleep so well with this anti-prozac cloud above me? 

Depression......what is it? Does it even exist? Is it a chemical imbalance, or is it purely psychological."

This made me think.  A good space out type thinking.  I wish I could sleep like that.  Or at all.

I'm impressed with myself. Can you believe I did a craft! And it isn't horridly ugly and I finished it. Amazing. I even sat still for like 4 hours. Oh here's a fun fact: that heart is all Marc Jacobs..it's his shirt, a dress, and a pair of shoes (not moon boots :( )
What slut! My girls rep TX hard too. Big ups to my mom's lameness for the shirts.
This beauty is hard to hate. I could just stand outside forever.
Here's what happens when we get bored...

I hardly can wait...

I just got back from Hallmark with Flex and can I just say, I LOVE that place!  I always liked cards, but now I totally have a reason to buy them more often.  I went in to buy two birthday card and ended up with that and a gang of other stuff.  Valentine's Day is gonna be rad.  I got the best cards ever!  They're beyond hot!  Only the best for my hos.  I'm tres excited.  Now I'm off to rinse the glitter from my hands.

I just took the fastest nap of my lifetime.  I had an hour before class and I was starting to get loopy, so I decided to just lay in my bed and chill.  I stayed awake until 3:30-ish.  Then I heard Madde come in and ask if I was ready to go at like 3:50. That time in the middle was lost. If it wasn't for Pascal, I wouldn't have even known I was sleeping.  It was weird, it makes me wonder how often I do that.
then hey fuck you! I rep hard bitches. That's all I got to say.

Do you remember that one time when that kid took Viagra and had an erection for like 6 hrs and couldn't get rid of it and his nipples where so sensitive they bled and everyone called him "erection boy" and made fun of him behind his back. Hehehehe....man, that shit was funny.

how it feels to open up and breathe.

Why can't all the nights be like this one???
Yeah, let's not!  It's snowing.  Like the ground is white. My car is covered. I don't know what to do. AND Connie threw 2 snowballs at me. Snow is not my friend. Not at all.

Just when you think things can't get worse, they do.  I was just thinking about how I'm not looking forward to break and I get a call from my mum saying someone broke into my house.  So now I'm left with even less then I expected.  Fucking hell, what else could happen?  Failed finals? Chrismukkah fire? Plane crash? Ok, I'm being dramatic, but damn it!! I'm allowed!  It's not that big of a deal, I mean it's just stuff, but fuck me.  Why can't shit like this not happen??? Why can't I ever win?!?!?  Who breaks through the front door??? Oy vey, I feel so bad for my mum.  She has no one and she's a bloody mess as usual.  At least she didn't cry this time.  This has been the best year ever in the Egeolu family.  I offically suck at life.
